metadata.title: Bald Eagle nest locations and productivity

creators.name: Wildlife Service (USFWS), Oil Spill Administration Office

metadata.description: Data Type: Birds;  Contains bald eagle nest locations and their productivity status for 1989 and 1990. Historical productivity data (1963-1990) is provided for Kodiak Island. Also includes an analysis of distance from nest to nearest shore. Scale is 1:63,360, 1:250,000 for the Alaska Peninsula.
